SummaryEnglish:
The Taoists believed that he had stood at the top of the world, and he could feel free in the future. But later in the day, the Taoists realized that it was difficult to avoid doom. There is a ruler over them, harvesting one era for an era.
These World Reaper rulers to keep their ambitions enslaving all races and spirits. These rulers, harvest Taoists, harvest the spirits of every world and destroy it. Although there is always a generation of every era that does not want to be harvested and constantly rebelled but fails at any time. Until… Ye Yu’s protagonist appears. When he opens the ancient scroll rolls she finds secrets. In this vast world, he continues to grow, experiencing love and friendship, purifying the filthy hearts of dust, and finally dealing with Rulers who harvest all worlds and spirits.
